(10, 'Over 1,000 corps members redeployed from Yobe', '', NULL, 'THE Yobe State coordinator  National Youth Service Corps  NYSC   Mr Ibrahim Lass  has said that more than 1 000 corps members redeployed out of a total number of 2 430 that were mobilised to undergo their one year service in the state  He  however  noted that in view of the security challenge in the state  corps members would only be deployed to serve in 11 out of the 17 local government areas in the state ', 'THE Yobe State coordinator  National Youth Service Corps  NYSC   Mr Ibrahim Lass  has said that more than 1 000 corps members redeployed out of a total number of 2 430 that were mobilised to undergo their one year service in the state  He  however  noted that in view of the security challenge in the state  corps members would only be deployed to serve in 11 out of the 17 local government areas in the state ', 'http://tribuneonlineng.com/content/over-1000-corps-members-redeployed-yobe', 1, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-06-23 10:20:26', '2015-06-23 10:20:26'),
(11, 'Alake commends Oodua Youths Congress, harps on agric entrepreneurship', '', NULL, 'THE Alake and paramount ruler of Egbaland  Oba Aremu Gbadebo  has lauded the vision of the Oodua Youths Congress  OYC  which is to liberate Yoruba youths from impoverishment and engaging them to embrace self advancement through diverse entrepreneurial support and empowerment programmes  The Alake of Egbaland praised the group when its leaders paid him a courtesy visit at his palace in Ake  Abeokuta  recently ', 'THE Alake and paramount ruler of Egbaland  Oba Aremu Gbadebo  has lauded the vision of the Oodua Youths Congress  OYC  which is to liberate Yoruba youths from impoverishment and engaging them to embrace self advancement through diverse entrepreneurial support and empowerment programmes  The Alake of Egbaland praised the group when its leaders paid him a courtesy visit at his palace in Ake  Abeokuta  recently ', 'http://tribuneonlineng.com/content/alake-commends-oodua-youths-congress-harps-agric-entrepreneurship', 1, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-06-23 10:20:26', '2015-06-23 10:20:26'),
