(13, 'Experts explain why Nigeria’s economic transformation remains elusive', '', NULL, 'Some experts in economic   development strategies    drawn from various tertiary institutions in the   South West    have explained why   transformation process     of the Nigerian economy   many   remain elusive   despite   all       government economic   policies  programmes and   strategies  The experts  at a national conference organized recently by the School of Arts and Social Sciences  Federal College of Education  Special  Oyo  expressed their views about the state of Nigerian economy and its transformation tendency ', 'Some experts in economic   development strategies    drawn from various tertiary institutions in the   South West    have explained why   transformation process     of the Nigerian economy   many   remain elusive   despite   all       government economic   policies  programmes and   strategies  The experts  at a national conference organized recently by the School of Arts and Social Sciences  Federal College of Education  Special  Oyo  expressed their views about the state of Nigerian economy and its transformation tendency ', 'http://tribuneonlineng.com/content/experts-explain-why-nigeria%E2%80%99s-economic-transformation-remains-elusive', 1, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-06-23 10:20:27', '2015-06-23 10:20:27'),
(14, 'Customers besiege banks for BVN exercise few days to deadline', '', NULL, 'Many bank customers in Makurdi  on Monday besieged their banks to collect their Bank Verification Number  BVN  a week to the deadline of the exercise  The News Agency of Nigeria  NAN  reports that the BVN is for biometric registration of all bank customers in the country  NAN report s that while many customers had done their registration  a good number is yet to comply with the Central Bank   s directive  A cross section of customers who spoke to NAN said that they could not participate in the exercise early enough because of their crowded schedules ', 'Many bank customers in Makurdi  on Monday besieged their banks to collect their Bank Verification Number  BVN  a week to the deadline of the exercise  The News Agency of Nigeria  NAN  reports that the BVN is for biometric registration of all bank customers in the country  NAN report s that while many customers had done their registration  a good number is yet to comply with the Central Bank   s directive  A cross section of customers who spoke to NAN said that they could not participate in the exercise early enough because of their crowded schedules ', 'http://tribuneonlineng.com/content/customers-besiege-banks-bvn-exercise-few-days-deadline', 1, 1, 1, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-06-23 10:20:27', '2015-06-23 10:20:27'),
